### <a id='shared'></a> Shared <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %> Development environments for VMware Tanzu Partners

<%= vars.company_name %> operates and manages a number of shared <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %> development environments for ISV partners to use in developing their product tiles.

To use your assigned environment:

1. Log in to <%= vars.company_name %> Tile Dashboard using the credentials that you use for [Partners Slack](https://pivotalpartners.slack.com/).

1. Click the environment assigned to you.

1. Log in to Tanzu Operations Manager with the given Tanzu Operations Manager URL and credentials.

1. Log in to Apps Manager or the cf CLI with the Cloud Foundry information provided on the same page.

If you would like to become a partner, visit the [VMware Partners website](https://www.vmware.com/partners.html). To check your partner status, visit the [Partner Locator](https://partnerlocator.vmware.com). If you cannot access the Partners Slack instance, email isv@pivotal.io.

